  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <head>¶To the fainting Friend.</head>
   <l>Thou weary art of doing good,</l>
   <l>Though I the same to losse of Blood.</l>
   <l>Reward is ioyn'd with Constancy,</l>
   <l>When Iudgment whips Apostacy.</l>
   <l>Memor esto vnde excideris &amp; Resipisce.</l>
</div>
